name: Tweedia
body:
### Welcome to Tweedia Pages.

Tweedia is a kind of GUI-base shell software specialized for analyzing results of called programs.

* Operaiton of Tweedia is validated on MacOSX(Snow Leoperd).
* Tweedia is a free software distributed under GPL.
